    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, separate 6 <strong>outer lettuce leaves</strong> per person,<strong> </strong>wash and dry with kitchen paper and shred the <strong>inner core[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p>",
