    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli relish</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]<strong> </span>sugar </strong>and 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[5 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and the juice of<strong> half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into wedges</p>",
